{"version":1,"entries":{"person_1972402_translations":{"at":1773369218132,"data":{"id":1972402,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kana Ichinose (市ノ瀬 加那, December 20) is a Japanese voice actress from Hokkaido. She is affiliated with Sigma Seven. She played her first main role in 2018 as Ichigo in the anime series Darling in the Franxx.","name":"Kana Ichinose","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"이치노세 카나","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"市之瀨加那是日本的女性聲優。出身於北海道，所屬公司為 Sigma Seven。","name":"市之瀨加那","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"市ノ瀬加那","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"市之濑加那（日语：市ノ瀬 加那／いちのせ かな Ichinose Kana，1996年12月20日—）是日本的女性声优、电视艺人。Sigma Seven所属。北海道出身。\n\n小时候就喜欢动画，但真正热爱起来是在初中一、二年级的时候，当时迷上了《网球王子》。成为声优的契机是从热爱动画后开始考虑投身于与动画相关的职业，并在思考自己的未来时，开始参加与此相关的学校的开放日活动，希望找到相关职业的出路。\n\n在其中一次参加声优课程的开放日活动中，她在自我介绍时用自己的真实声音回答，然后被讲师问到“那是你的自然声音吗？”，她回答说“是的”，讲师说：“我觉得你非常适合这个职业”，于是开始强烈地考虑成为一名声优。\n\n札幌放送艺术专门学校出身。2016年4月加入Sigma Seven事务所。2018年1月在《DARLING in the FRANXX》中为莓配音，首次声演主要角色。2021年3月获得第15回声优奖新人女优赏。2021年11月1日，从所属事务所Sigma Seven e升格至Sigma Seven。2023年3月获得第18回声优奖主演声优赏。\n\n爱好是独自旅行、观察天空、看电影。中小学生时代爱好篮球，现在仍是特长。资格有危险物处理者丙级、演示制作检定3级、日语文字处理检定3级、信息处理技能检定2级、个人电脑速度认定3级。","name":"市之濑加那","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kana Ichinose","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Kana Ichinose (市ノ瀬 加那, 20 de diciembre) es una actriz de voz japonesa de Hokkaido. Está afiliada a Sigma Seven. Desempeñó su primer papel principal en el 2018 como Ichigo en la serie de anime Darling in the Franxx.","name":"Kana Ichinose","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"คานะ อิจิโนเซะ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kana Ičinose","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кана Ічіносе","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кана Итиносэ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kana Ichinose","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"市之瀨加那是日本的女性聲優。出身於北海道，所屬公司為 Sigma Seven。","name":"市之瀨加那","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Kana Ichinose (市ノ瀬 加那) est une doubleuse japonaise originaire de Obihiro. Elle a joué son premier rôle principal en 2018 dans le rôle d'Ichigo dans la série animée Darling in the Franxx.","name":"Kana Ichinose","primary":false}}]}},"movie_787747_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1773039162639,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/yGH7ke2rbeSI4IZx90UzIrMlWLq.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":27,"name":"Phim Kinh Dị"},{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"},{"id":53,"name":"Phim Gây Cấn"}],"homepage":"","id":787747,"imdb_id":"tt12706836","origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Shell","overview":"","popularity":7.2986,"poster_path":"/2XBNS8DxMFP7qOoTOY7cc8OYFwI.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":22146,"logo_path":"/v37N1mFeXNQfvPankg3feBhVvM7.png","name":"Black Bear Pictures","origin_country":"US"},{"id":137619,"logo_path":null,"name":"Love & Squalor Pictures","origin_country