":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"中國內地女歌手，演員。2016 年，參加芒果 TV 網絡選秀娛樂節目《2016 超級女聲》，自此正式出道。2017 年 3 月，發佈個人首支原創單曲《雛菊》；4 月，為愛情劇《狐狸的夏天》演唱了主題曲《在一起》 ；5 月，發佈個人第二支原創單曲《輕眠》；6 月，發佈原創單曲《時光流沙》；同年 11 月，發佈個人首張 mini 專輯《初次見你那一天》。2019 年參加《明日之子水晶時代》節目。2020 年 7 月，與好友汪睿合作《遠行的煙火》；同年發表原創單曲《走向你的時候》《打包包》《此刻》。2021 年 4 月 1 日，主演的古裝劇《夫人，大可不必》於芒果 TV 正式播出。","name":"彭雅琦","primary":false}}]}},"person_5416890_translations":{"at":1773319436392,"data":{"id":5416890,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mohammad Eid","primary":true}}]}},"person_1937533_translations":{"at":1773384111926,"data":{"id":1937533,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jeon Jong-seo (born July 5, 1994), also known as Rachel Jun, is a South Korean actress. She made her acting debut in a leading role in the acclaimed thriller film Burning (2018). She next starred in the film The Call (2020) for which she won the Baeksang Arts Award for Best Actress. She starred in the English language film Mona Lisa and the Blood Moon (2021) and in the Netflix series Money Heist: Korea – Joint Economic Area (2022).","name":"Jeon Jong-seo","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"全鐘瑞","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"전종서","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"全钟瑞（韩语：전종서，1994年7月5日－），韩国女演员，出道前就读世宗大学电影艺术系。2018年参与李沧东执导的《燃烧烈爱》的试镜，并顺利获得角色，与刘亚仁、史蒂文·连共同主演。该片入围第71届戛纳影展正式竞赛电影。全钟瑞亦凭海美一角，入围多个电影奖项。2021年，全钟瑞凭《声命线索》夺得第57届百想艺术大奖的电影部门女子最优秀演技奖（最佳女主角），出道仅三年已获韩国电影最高荣誉的奖项。并在同年7月入围第26届春史电影奖的最佳女主角奖","name":"全钟瑞","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DK","iso_639_1":"da","name":"Dansk","english_name":"Danish","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jeon Jong-seo","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jun Jong-seo","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"全鍾瑞（韓語：전종서，1994 年 7 月 5 日－），韓國女演員，出道前就讀世宗大學電影藝術系。2018 年參與李滄東執導的《燒失樂園》的試鏡，並順利獲得角色，與劉亞仁、史蒂文·聯共同主演。該片入圍第 71 屆戛納影展正式競賽電影。全鍾瑞亦憑海美一角，入圍多個電影獎項。2021 年，全鍾瑞憑《The Call：超時空通話》奪得第 57 屆百想藝術大獎的電影部門女子最優秀演技獎（最佳女主角），出道僅三年已獲韓國電影最高榮譽的獎項。並在同年 7 月入圍第 26 屆春史電影獎的最佳女主角獎","name":"全鐘瑞","primary":false}}]}},"person_87352_translations":{"at":1773405758147,"data":{"id":87352,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Nikitin Dheer is an Indian actor known for his powerful villainous roles in Bollywood and television. Born on March 17, 1980, in Mumbai, India, he is the son of veteran actor Pankaj Dheer. Nikitin made his Bollywood debut with Jodhaa Akbar (2008), portraying the fierce Mughal warrior Sharifuddin Hussain. He gained widespread recognition as the intimidating Thangaballi in Chennai Express (2013) and appeared in action-packed films like Dabangg 2 (2012), Housefull 3 (2016), and Shershaah (2021). On television, he impressed audiences with his roles in Ishqbaaaz and Naagin 3. Known for his towering physique and commanding screen presence, Nikitin has also showcased his adventurous side in reality shows like Khatron Ke Khilad